title: Mr Moane, on the phone, in the zone
description: Ah yes, this old kettle of fish. Originating in San Francisco, this meme was born due to Felix absent-mindedly singing Hoodie Allen’s hit single 'No Interruption', but with the rhyming chorus lyrics replaced with 'Mr Moane', 'On the phone', 'In the Zone'. Yes he heard… No we didn’t speak about it.
